        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 10. — A-D, Eucalathis magna Cooper, 1981, ventral, dorsal, lateral and anterior views of complete specimen (MNHN IB-2013-60), South Madagascar, sector of Manantenina, stn DW 3529, 402-407 m; E-O, Eucalathis daphneae n. sp., North-West Madagascar, MIRIKY, SEM: E, inner view of ventral valve (MNHN IB- 2013-62), paratype, West of Cap d’Ambre, stn DW 3196, 238-249 m; F-J, dorsal view of complete specimen, enlargement of umbonal part (G) and anterior view to show rounded ribs (H), and inner view of dorsal valve (I, J) of the same specimen to show cardinalia and loop, holotype (MNHN IB-2013-61), West of Nosy Be, stn DW 3234, 187-247 m; K-O, inner view of dorsal valve (MNHN IB-2013-63), enlargement (L) and tilted (M) views of posterior part,and a fragment of incomplete transverse band (O), paratype, stn DW 3196, 238-249 m. Scale bars: A-D, 5 mm; E, F, H, I, K, 2 mm; G, J, L,1 mm; M, 500 µm; O, 200 µm." ;
